to go with me, but...

269
00:10:49,025 --> 00:10:52,361
But, unfortunately, he got
involved in the family business.

270
00:10:54,113 --> 00:10:56,490
I know you were the one
who put my mother in prison.

271
00:10:56,782 --> 00:10:58,326
