It's so frustrating.

294
00:11:54,632 --> 00:11:56,550
Well, there is one
thing I'm waiting on.

295
00:11:56,759 --> 00:11:58,344
- But I thought you
just said we had nada.
- Well,

296
00:11:58,552 --> 00:11:59,553
so the only thing
we know for sure

