00:12:24,078 --> 00:12:26,455
Satellite imaging takes
sporadic photos of,

309
00:12:26,664 --> 00:12:28,249
well, everything, so...

310
00:12:28,457 --> 00:12:29,583
So there may be footage
of the killer

