00:13:24,847 --> 00:13:26,390
Mm-hmm, mm-hmm.
Totally understand.

336
00:13:26,599 --> 00:13:28,017
- I got this.
- Perfect.

337
00:13:28,559 --> 00:13:30,102
All right, let's give 'em
another scenario.

