They're not dandelions;
they're jellyfish.

364
00:14:31,997 --> 00:14:33,624
What? Jellyfish?

365
00:14:34,124 --> 00:14:34,834
LUCIFER:
Right, yes.

366
00:14:35,042 --> 00:14:36,377
Well, I'm simply saying that

367
00:14:36,585 --> 00:14:38,796
we should be focusing on
more pressing criminal issues.

