384
00:15:22,715 --> 00:15:23,757
This is my sister Kathleen.

385
00:15:23,966 --> 00:15:24,967
Hi. How ya doin'?

386
00:15:25,175 --> 00:15:26,719
Friendliest serial killers ever.

387
00:15:26,927 --> 00:15:29,221
AVA: Oh, that's hilarious.
We're not killers.

388
00:15:29,471 --> 00:15:30,472
(laughs):
God, no.

389
00:15:30,681 --> 00:15:32,266
We run Dandy
Lyon Cleaners.

390
00:15:32,474 --> 00:15:34,685
Lyon's our last name.
Get it?

391
00:15:35,019 --> 00:15:37,438
We take care of crime scenes,
dead body removals.

392
00:15:37,646 --> 00:15:38,606
All the icky stuff.

393
