assemble the sword,

510
00:19:58,073 --> 00:19:59,867
yes, I want to cut through
the gates, blah, blah,

511
00:20:00,075 --> 00:20:01,994
but then I was just gonna
kick Mum into Heaven

512
00:20:02,202 --> 00:20:03,620
